Penguins control the draw,
drop it into the Chicago end.

01:27:42.880 --> 01:27:44.720
Jagr will carry it in.

01:28:59.800 --> 01:29:04.400
Both net-minders coming up tough here.
McEachern has it again!

01:29:04.440 --> 01:29:06.320
Psst.

01:29:19.120 --> 01:29:21.040
Aah!

01:29:22.120 --> 01:29:24.720
Aaaah!

01:29:26.080 --> 01:29:29.440
